{"id": "ChIJe7ZRYAB_j4AR7Me42C4yARE", "rating": 4.2, "userRatingCount": 256, "displayName": {"text": "Tadaima Mission", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJe7ZRYAB_j4AR7Me42C4yARE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21KbVRXaEhha1pKU2xwUlJYUk1SRTF4U2pWZlpXYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I really loved the pistachio cream—so rich, nutty, and creamy. The matcha was pretty good too; you can tell it’s high quality. I also enjoyed the tempura sando! It’s made with really good quality prawns which was a bit of a surprise. The only thing is, it’s kinda pricey at around $27.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I really loved the pistachio cream—so rich, nutty, and creamy. The matcha was pretty good too; you can tell it’s high quality. I also enjoyed the tempura sando! It’s made with really good quality prawns which was a bit of a surprise. The only thing is, it’s kinda pricey at around $27.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Ernice Ho", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105300262520613347472/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVXzat0XQF3xDysbJsna0945XRbvzZpyA8idTMg7i_2ln4Rrjik=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-17T02:57:43.489825887Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21KbVRXaEhha1pKU2xwUlJYUk1SRTF4U2pWZlpXYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21KbVRXaEhha1pKU2xwUlJYUk1SRTF4U2pWZlpXYxAB!2m1!1s0x808f7f006051b67b:0x1101322ed8b8c7ec"}, {"name": "places/ChIJe7ZRYAB_j4AR7Me42C4yARE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tWcWNFdFFURGg2VjA5U1IzZEdhMmxwVldScmVGRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 1, "text": {"text": "My friend described the oat milk matcha latte as \"swamp water with 25 pumps of syrup\". It was somehow both too sweet yet also bitter. Worst matcha I've had in SF, but the hojicha was decent. I think people only like this place for the food but I didn't see any vegan options.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "My friend described the oat milk matcha latte as \"swamp water with 25 pumps of syrup\". It was somehow both too sweet yet also bitter. Worst matcha I've had in SF, but the hojicha was decent. I think people only like this place for the food but I didn't see any vegan options.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Kristina Femal", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108314476728056138700/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLnUPA1hgWl8gOqNB1LAWKV2d7KH1-OgBR-LS59FwCurt5qjgm0=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-25T04:51:58.737628972Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tWcWNFdFFURGg2VjA5U1IzZEdhMmxwVldScmVGRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tWcWNFdFFURGg2VjA5U1IzZEdhMmxwVldScmVGRRAB!2m1!1s0x808f7f006051b67b:0x1101322ed8b8c7ec"}, {"name": "places/ChIJe7ZRYAB_j4AR7Me42C4yARE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2sxc1NFSkliR2R0WWxwd2VXbEtTSEUzTTJWaFprRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "The matchas and sandos at Tadaima are hella yummy! Sandos are a good size and will keep you full. Def worth the price! The salted cheese matcha is my favorite. They know how to make a good salted cheese here! This location is cool if you’re like picking up and eating somewhere else because there’s only room for like 3 people to eat inside and very few tables and chairs outside. Their Marina location is perfect to hang out in!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The matchas and sandos at Tadaima are hella yummy! Sandos are a good size and will keep you full. Def worth the price! The salted cheese matcha is my favorite. They know how to make a good salted cheese here! This location is cool if you’re like picking up and eating somewhere else because there’s only room for like 3 people to eat inside and very few tables and chairs outside. Their Marina location is perfect to hang out in!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Sarah Rebello", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113904756335155619460/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXcW5pSexm1186uJAEgnzbvlEmJhfuR-0m5DaSPWIH6Dgujbzdl=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-02T18:28:20.558066557Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2sxc1NFSkliR2R0WWxwd2VXbEtTSEUzTTJWaFprRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2sxc1NFSkliR2R0WWxwd2VXbEtTSEUzTTJWaFprRRAB!2m1!1s0x808f7f006051b67b:0x1101322ed8b8c7ec"}, {"name": "places/ChIJe7ZRYAB_j4AR7Me42C4yARE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25KdVJYUXljMnBxWm5oS1dIVTNPRUprZVcxRGFFRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Cute little Japanese matcha, sandwich, onigiri eatery on the outskirts of the Mission District... Pleasant surprise, as it's located in the middle of the neighborhood, but the drinks were good and the food was decent as well..... It's a great neighborhood find, and will be on my list of repeats next time I'm on the area.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Cute little Japanese matcha, sandwich, onigiri eatery on the outskirts of the Mission District... Pleasant surprise, as it's located in the middle of the neighborhood, but the drinks were good and the food was decent as well..... It's a great neighborhood find, and will be on my list of repeats next time I'm on the area.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Dennis W.", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102599720402520504627/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYgbPIy8NygjS85rDIkuryZA0dBgPZSdQQcE9JEyp7sgCvLbE3=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba7"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-10T20:41:30.447300972Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25KdVJYUXljMnBxWm5oS1dIVTNPRUprZVcxRGFFRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25KdVJYUXljMnBxWm5oS1dIVTNPRUprZVcxRGFFRRAB!2m1!1s0x808f7f006051b67b:0x1101322ed8b8c7ec"}, {"name": "places/ChIJe7ZRYAB_j4AR7Me42C4yARE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2sxTk9YVm1abGd4V0Uxb2VWWXRXRFJWWW5STFNFRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "7 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Always wanted to try the Japanese cream sandwich and encountered this place today by accident! Fruits are very fresh, bread is soft, the flavor is just as I imagined how it would be so I’m very happy. The matcha latte is on the thicker side which I personally don’t like but that’s just a preference thing. The pistachio cream is very good tho.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Always wanted to try the Japanese cream sandwich and encountered this place today by accident! Fruits are very fresh, bread is soft, the flavor is just as I imagined how it would be so I’m very happy. The matcha latte is on the thicker side which I personally don’t like but that’s just a preference thing. The pistachio cream is very good tho.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Amanda Liu", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115691174480067777186/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWlqt2MM9K2acm6l1JCEA6VHBYkZYtP4pfMc1qQJJVpOfPBP3cHug=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-11-25T08:11:15.671829886Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2sxTk9YVm1abGd4V0U